snippet.title: Commodore 64 -=Veggies vs Undead=-
snippet.description:
Commodore 64 =Veggies vs Undead=
***
Saberman&IndieRetroNews.com present: Veggies vs Undead

The zombies are on the loose, actually they are already in front of your property. The only thing between your brain and their insatiable appetite is your front lawn. Luckily you just acquired an assortment of powerful flower seeds. Plant them fast and smart to protect your home.

Author: drmortalwombat
Programming: Dr. Mortal Wombat
Music: Crisps

Source:
